            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E7%A7%8B%E5%AD%A3%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%91%E6%9C%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E7%A7%8B%E5%AD%A3%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%91%E6%9C%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我国多地进入秋季过敏高发期#</span></a>【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%93%AA%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E8%A6%81%E5%8F%8A%E6%97%B6%E5%B0%B1%E5%8C%BB%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%93%AA%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E8%A6%81%E5%8F%8A%E6%97%B6%E5%B0%B1%E5%8C%BB%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#过敏出现哪种症状要及时就医#</span></a>】专家提醒，目前我国多地已进入了秋季“过敏高发期”。一旦出现过敏症状，需注意个人卫生，不要用手随意去抠鼻、揉眼睛。当过敏症状严重且难以自行缓解时，要及时就医，避免引起并发症！ <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4945818675773471" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a>（央视新闻） <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hhvwk5n74wj624w179u0x02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/neDQYdW4lx088AHta4Qo0104120157OY0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1694784191&amp;ssig=bpM5Fyexb8&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/DIx8L2x7lx088AHsFeLu01041200ydUb0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=169478